Items.Title: Manhattan
Items.Subtitle: Martini Glass
Items.Description: A Manhattan is a cocktail made with whiskey, sweet vermouth, and bitters. Commonly used whiskeys include rye, Canadian whisky, bourbon, blended whiskey and Tennessee whiskey.
